13 within the four-year period immediately preceding the date the independent
14 expenditure was made.
15
16 SECTION 4. Arkansas Code § 7-9-402, concerning definitions for
17 disclosure matters referred to voters, is amended to add additional
18 subdivisions to read as follows:
19 (13) “Directly or indirectly” means acting either alone or 10
20 jointly with, through, or on behalf of any other:
21 (A) Ballot question committee;
22 (B) Legislative question committee;
23 (C) Political action committee;
24 (D) Organization;
25 (E) Person; or
26 (F) Other entity;
27 (14) “Foreign national” means:
28 (A) An individual who is not a citizen or lawful permanent
29 resident of the United States;
30 (B) A government or subdivision of a foreign country; or
31 (C) A foreign political party;
32 (D) An entity, including without limitation a partnership,
33 association, corporation, organization, or other combination of persons, that
34 is organized under the laws of, or has its principal place of business in, a
35 foreign country; or
36 (E) A partnership, association, corporation, or
