1 organization, which is wholly or majority owned by a foreign national,
2 unless:
3 (i) A contribution or expenditure the entity makes
4 derives entirely from funds generated by the entity’s operations; and
5 (ii) All decisions concerning the contribution or
6 expenditure are made by individuals who are United States citizens or
7 permanent residents, except for setting overall budget amounts;
8 (15) "Independent expenditure" means the same as defined in § 7-
9 6-201;
10 (16) "Preliminary activity" includes:
11 (A) Conducting a poll;
